<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Konrad IX. von Weinsberg</head><p>Der Rat kündigt wegen des Überfalls auf Nürnberger Kaufleute Hans Maurer, Diener der Stadt, an.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_294" id="146v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_294_r2l25"><expan>Jt<ex>em</ex></expan> <expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> cʒü <expan>Weinſp<ex>er</ex>g</expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_294_r2l27">Edler <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> / Als Jr vns nehſt verſchrıbt <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> nam <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_294_r2l28">als <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>geſcheh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> iſt / darauf wir <expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>n</expan> gnaden <expan>vvid<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_294_r2l29">
<del rend="strikethrough">ant </del> <expan>ſchrıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / daʒ <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>botſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>d<ex>er</ex>ſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſache <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> beÿ <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_294_r2l30">gnedıgen <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> von Meincʒ 
<del rend="strikethrough">heten </del> were / vnd nicht weſten wie </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_294_r2l31">die <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> ſeinen <expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſcheıden vvürde / Alſo daʒ wir ew cʒü <expan>d<ex>er</ex>ſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_294_r2l32">cʒeit kein völlig <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchreıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> künden / . Nu danken wir </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_294_r2l33"><expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſölıchs <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchreibens</expan> vnd ewrs güten willen <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> mit </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_294_r2l34"><expan>gancʒe<ex>m</ex></expan> fleiʒʒ / vnd <expan>ſchick<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> cʒu <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> edel / <expan>Hanſ<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>Mawr<ex>er</ex></expan> / </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_294_r2l35"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>dıen<ex>er</ex></expan> mit <expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan> davon cʒe <expan>red<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / vnd <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> etc / </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_294_r2l36"><expan>gelawbſbr<ex>ief</ex></expan> / </ab>
<note place="bottomcentral"><ab facs="#facs_294_r2l37"><expan>Jt<ex>em</ex></expan> einen ſölıchen <expan>br<ex>ief</ex></expan> auf <expan>Markh<ex>a</ex>rt<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>VValt<ex>man</ex></expan> </ab></note>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_294" id="146v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>It<ex>em</ex></expan>
<expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan>, <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> czü
                                <expan>Weinsp<ex>er</ex>g</expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab>Edler <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan>, als ir uns nehst verschribt <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> nam
                                <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan>, als <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> den
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gescheh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ist, darauf wir
                            <expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>n</expan> gnaden <expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, daz <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>botsch<ex>aft</ex></expan>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>d<ex>er</ex>selb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sache
                            <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> bey <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
                        gnedigen <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> von Meincz were und nicht westen,
                        wie die <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> seinen <expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        scheiden würde, also daz wir ew czü
                            <expan>d<ex>er</ex>selb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> czeit kein völlig
                                <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>schreib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> künden. Nu danken wir
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sölichs <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schreibens</expan>
                        und ewrs güten willen <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> mit
                                <expan>gancze<ex>m</ex></expan> fleizz und
                            <expan>schick<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> czu <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> edel
                                <expan>Hans<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>Mawr<ex>er</ex></expan>, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan>, mit <expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan> davon cze <expan>red<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und
                                <expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> etc.
                            <expan>Gelawbsbr<ex>ief</ex></expan>. <app>
<note place="bottomcentral"><expan>It<ex>em</ex></expan> einen sölichen
                                        <expan>br<ex>ief</ex></expan> auf
                                        <expan>Markh<ex>a</ex>rt<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>Walt<ex>man</ex></expan>.</note>
</app></ab></div>
</div></body>
